    <h1 style="font-size:40px;font-family:Segoe Script;">How to Fold an Easy Origami Bulldog</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<br><br><br>

<center><p>These instructions will show you how to fold an easy origami bulldog. You’ll need to use a few somewhat more complicated folds to make this model. 
If you have trouble at any point check out our <a href="/startHere" style="text-decoration:none;">Beginner’s Guide</a> to familiarize yourself with all the basic folds.</p></center>

<br><br><br>

<div class="container">
<div class="card">
<center><div class="row">
 	 	<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			<img src="/img/BullDog/1.jpg" width="300" height="300">
 		</div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			<img src="/img/BullDog/2.jpg" width="300" height="300">
 	        </div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
   			 <img src="/img/BullDog/3.jpg" width="300" height="300">
 		</div>
	</div></center>
	<center><div class="row">
 	 	<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			<p><b>Step 1)</b> Fold the right corner of the paper about halfway towards the centre.</p>
 		</div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
   			 <p><b>Step 2)</b> Fold the tip of the top layer of paper back over to the right.</p>
 	        </div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			 <p><b>Step 3)</b> Mountain Fold the paper in half.</p>
 		</div>
	</div></center>
	<center><div class="row">
		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			<img src="/img/BullDog/4.jpg" width="300" height="300">
 		</div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			<img src="/img/BullDog/5.jpg" width="300" height="300">
 	        </div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
   			 <img src="/img/BullDog/6.jpg" width="300" height="300">
 		</div>
	</div></center>
	<center><div class="row">
 	 	<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			<p><b>Step 4)</b> Fold the paper in half along the dotted line.</p>
 		</div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
   			 <p><b>Step 5)</b> Open the top flap of paper over to the right and Squash Fold it flat.</p>
 	        </div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			 <p><b>Step 6)</b> Fold both sides of the diamond shape to the centre along the dotted lines and then unfold them.</p>
 		</div>
	</div></center>
	<center><div class="row">
		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			<img src="/img/BullDog/7.jpg" width="300" height="300">
 		</div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			<img src="/img/BullDog/8.jpg" width="300" height="300">
 	        </div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
   			 <img src="/img/BullDog/9.jpg" width="300" height="300">
 		</div>
	</div></center>
	<center><div class="row">
 	 	<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			<p><b>Step 7)</b> Lift up the paper along the dotted line, push in the sides along the existing creases and make a Petal Fold.</p>
 		</div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
   			 <p><b>Step 8)</b> Fold the top flap of paper down along the dotted line.</p>
 	        </div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			 <p><b>Step 9)</b> Fold both sides in along the dotted lines.</p>
 		</div>
	</div></center>
	<center><div class="row">
		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			<img src="/img/BullDog/10.jpg" width="300" height="300">
 		</div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			<img src="/img/BullDog/11.jpg" width="300" height="300">
 	        </div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
   			 <img src="/img/BullDog/12.jpg" width="300" height="300">
 		</div>
	</div></center>
	<center><div class="row">
 	 	<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			<p><b>Step 10)</b> Mountain Fold the paper along the dotted line.</p>
 		</div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
   			 <p><b>Step 11)</b> Fold the paper down along the dotted line.</p>
 	        </div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			 <p><b>Step 12)</b> Fold the top layer of paper up and inside the model.</p>
 		</div>
	</div></center>
	<center><div class="row">
		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			<img src="/img/BullDog/13.jpg" width="300" height="300">
 		</div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			<img src="/img/BullDog/14.jpg" width="300" height="300">
 	        </div>
	</div></center>
	<center><div class="row">
 	 	<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			<p><b>Step 13)</b> Fold the other layers of paper up along the dotted lines and behind the model.</p>
 		</div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
   			 <p><b>The completed bulldog</b></p>
 	        </div>
	</div></center>
